{"name":"Replicate contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive without manual work","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"weeks","triggerAtDay":[1],"triggerAtHour":9}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"971d5156-d71f-436e-9436-ab049ec6ce75","name":"Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"6607d892-24f2-40d8-b505-c8ea4c1ef5ac","name":"contactId","value":"={{ $json.body?.contactId || $json.body?.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"7f70af97-6b28-47fd-9447-1e8c9509128b","name":"kind","value":"={{ $json.body?.type || 'default' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"b1e678ae-e07c-4853-b063-c3c3a72becbe","name":"payload","value":"={{ JSON.stringify($json.body || $json) }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"b44e29da-58d3-4854-b52c-33aee2c09bc8","name":"Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"22d7434d-937c-4893-826d-4bfc228301ce","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"created","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"created"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"a0662f16-ce1e-4327-90ee-67c33a72aa87","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"updated","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"updated"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"d9eddab6-3039-400a-a7c6-835ba19028fd","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"deleted","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"deleted"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"2b151382-a36e-4a91-b22e-9fa686859b48","name":"Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[702,130],"id":"a5cb8e6b-8232-488d-a896-66661d1e15ba","name":"Handle 'created' → HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[1026,640],"id":"b6cfcca2-6c49-4844-9e8a-18b651138d8d","name":"Handle 'updated' → HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[1350,1150],"id":"912c0136-d457-4723-ae03-f69a7718023c","name":"Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[1674,1660],"id":"6a39314d-1300-4cab-b2f4-54a0b31e14fd","name":"Log Unrecognized Kind","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[2322,400],"id":"a4c21d3a-39e0-4cdd-8667-dba4bf537269","name":"Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"475ea315-b0ce-4dc3-fbfc-588d2ab40733","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Map to Canonical Schema\n\nShapes the item: writes `contactId`, `kind`, `payload`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Route by Event Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"268662ff-07ea-0dd3-a02f-91edbed8b8fc","name":"Note: Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: created, updated, deleted + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'created' → HubSpot · ②→ Handle 'updated' → HubSpot · ③→ Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot · ④→ Log Unrecognized Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0151a010-1229-102a-2de6-886d04c59e8f","name":"Note: Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'created' → HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"ca927919-0563-50bf-872b-fa90e68c149d","name":"Note: Handle 'created' → HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'updated' → HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"73fa9293-3bb9-0ee7-0c31-fdadab419d8f","name":"Note: Handle 'updated' → HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"7849bb3a-4dc0-3437-3b2f-dfbe9d6beab1","name":"Note: Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Unrecognized Kind\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1780],"id":"53e4ff0e-e68c-e3c3-b2d3-ed2ccab75b85","name":"Note: Log Unrecognized Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Consolidate Handling\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"d861bf8f-6368-d92c-134d-37e7171d8dd4","name":"Note: Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Replicate contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nReplicate contacts across systems with HubSpot and Google Drive without manual work. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual deal updates is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'created' → HubSpot → Consolidate Handling\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to two-system sync without manual effort\n- Anyone automating deal updates in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: HubSpot private-app token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"b117d568-07c6-b031-f64e-3bc6e7d06f11","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your deal updates process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"e6324d82-a49f-53bf-44b9-e7cab804067b","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Map to Canonical Schema","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Map to Canonical Schema":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Handle 'created' → HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'updated' → HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Unrecognized Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'created' → HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'updated' → HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Handle 'deleted' → HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Log Unrecognized Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":3}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"f43de039-331e-4f4f-94bb-2e84b0b26cab","id":"FDX08076"}